      <title>加密游说团体为美国大选筹集资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/crypto-lobby-bolsters-war-chest-for-us-elections-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加密货币行业继续推动制定更有利的监管规定，加密货币游说团体在 11 月美国总统和国会选举之前进一步增加了资金储备。区块链协会首席执行官克里斯汀·史密斯 (Kristin Smith) 与卡罗琳·海德 (Caroline Hyde) 一起参加“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/crypto-lobby-bolsters-war-chest-for-us-elections-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红海中断导致运费上涨，马士基上调利润预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/maersk-raises-profit-forecast-as-red-sea-disruption-boosts-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球贸易的风向标马士基航运有限公司上调了全年利润预期，称红海拥堵对全球供应线的影响比之前预期的要大，从而推高了运费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/maersk-raises-profit-forecast-as-red-sea-disruption-boosts-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:32:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙澳大利亚液化天然气工厂停产加剧全球供应困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/chevron-s-australian-lng-plant-outage-adds-to-global-supply-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，澳大利亚一个重要液化天然气出口设施的部分生产暂停，由于挪威的管道问题导致欧洲的天然气流量减少，全球供应可能进一步收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/chevron-s-australian-lng-plant-outage-adds-to-global-supply-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称美国蓝筹公司的健康状况比杠杆率所暗示的要好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/us-investment-grade-companies-are-healthier-than-leverage-implies-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行称，受到评级上调、盈利增长加快和利润率提高的推动，美国企业发现从投资级市场借款更加便宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/us-investment-grade-companies-are-healthier-than-leverage-implies-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利警告称美国大选将威胁热门宏观交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/morgan-stanley-warns-us-elections-threaten-popular-macro-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利表示，由于投资者争相削减风险敞口，美国大选不确定性加剧可能会危及今年一些最受欢迎的宏观交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/morgan-stanley-warns-us-elections-threaten-popular-macro-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比尔·阿克曼的潘兴广场计划为美国基金筹集 250 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/ackman-s-pershing-square-targets-raising-25-billion-for-us-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 旗下的潘兴广场 (Pershing Square) 计划募集 250 亿美元用于一只新的封闭式基金，预计将吸引美国散户投资者的兴趣，这将使该公司管理的付费资产规模增加一倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/ackman-s-pershing-square-targets-raising-25-billion-for-us-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 17:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
